data.description: Very nice home, new paint, very clean and move in ready. Home features a large country kitchen with lots of work space and cabinets. The bedrooms have a split plan.Large separate laundry room. Living room leads to back yard that is awsome with a darling gazebo, matching dog house and utility building surrounded by a cement block wall with a double gate. Pretty landscaping and tree's in the front and back.
